      "rationale": "Titanium alloy (Ti-6Al-4V) modeled with bilinear isotropic hardening; cortical bone surrogate modeled as linear elastic per ASTM F1717 UHMWPE block specification. Frictional contact (mu=0.2) at screw-rod interface. Sensitivity analysis confirmed model form adequate for stiffness and yield force prediction."
