      "rationale": "Eleven non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs assembled from production lots tested: six at Lab A (FDA CDRH) and five at Lab B (DePuy Synthes). Lot traceability documented. Between-lab variability assessed; coefficient of variation < 5% for stiffness."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
