      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test conditions span the clinical loading envelope or multiple load levels are evaluated.",
      "rationale": "ASTM F1717 specifies a single quasi-static compression-bending condition. Only one load configuration was evaluated; physiological loading variability not spanned. This factor is below required level. Risk accepted given that F1717 is the regulatory standard for this device class and the model is used exclusively for regulatory submission under this standard."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
