      "rationale": "FEA boundary conditions replicate F1717 fixture geometry (UHMWPE blocks, loading nose, support geometry) as measured by CMM. Material properties assigned from same lot certificates used to characterize physical specimens. Equivalency matrix completed and reviewed."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
